Join CANSA Lowveld and various motorbike chapters on October 31 as they drive from Pretoria to Mbombela as part of an awareness campaign. The route will bring everyone together at the CANSA Lowveld offices at 6 Annecke Street by 14:00. “The bikers will be riding for CANSA, raising awareness and funds for patient care and support starting from Polokwane via Pretoria, Ermelo to Mbombela,” said Ramphosi Shawe, CANSA Lowveld service delivery coordinator. For more information about this event, please contact Tiyani Hlabangwane on 083-324-6163. ALSO READ: Join CANSA Lowveld for free breast examinations